description: Overview, Disk, Network, Memory and Docker Containers

targets.query:
from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "system" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r._field == "uptime"
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "system" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "n_cpus"
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "mem" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r._field == "total"
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r["_measurement"] == "swap" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "total"
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "mem" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r._field == "used_percent"
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "cpu" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r.cpu == "cpu-total" and
    r._field == "usage_idle"
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value * -1.0 + 100.0 }))
  |> toFloat()
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "docker" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    (r["_field"] == "n_containers" or r["_field"] == "n_containers_paused" or r["_field"] == "n_containers_running" or r["_field"] == "n_containers_stopped")
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "docker" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "n_images"
  )
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r["_measurement"] == "diskio" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "io_time" and
    r["name"] =~ /^[a-z]+$/
  )
  |> derivative(nonNegative: true, unit: 1ms)
  |> group(columns: ["name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 60s, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "disk" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    (r["_field"] == "free" or r["_field"] == "total")
  )
  |> group(columns: ["device"])
  |> pivot(
    rowKey:["_time"],
    columnKey: ["_field"],
    valueColumn: "_value"
  )
  |> last(column: "_time")
  |> group()
  |> keep(columns: ["free", "total", "device"])

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop:v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r._measurement == "disk" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r._field == "used_percent"
  )
  |> group(columns: ["device"])
  |> last()

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "cpu" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "usage_idle" and
    r["cpu"] != "cpu-total"
  )
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({ r with _value: r._value * -1.0 + 100.0 }))
  |> toFloat()
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "cpu"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "mem" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "used_percent"
  )
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "mem" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "used"
  )
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "docker_container_mem" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "usage_percent"
  )
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "container_name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "docker_container_mem" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "usage"
  )
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "container_name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) =>
    r["_measurement"] == "swap" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "used_percent"
  )
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "net" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    (r["_field"] == "bytes_recv" or r["_field"] == "bytes_sent")
  )
  |> derivative()
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: mean, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "mean")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "docker_container_net" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "tx_bytes"
  )
  |> derivative(nonNegative: true)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "container_name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "last")

from(bucket: v.defaultBucket)
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => 
    r["_measurement"] == "docker_container_net" and
    r.host == "${host}" and
    r["_field"] == "rx_bytes"
  )
  |> derivative(nonNegative: true)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value", "container_name"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: v.windowPeriod, fn: last, createEmpty: false)
  |> yield(name: "last")
